%% Dashboard Access — signup, invite acceptance, login, role gating
%% Single business per account. Roles: Owner / Admin / Staff. No MFA.
flowchart TD
    Start([User visits app]) --> Entry{Entry point?}

    %% --- Self-serve signup (creates the business) ---
    Entry -->|Sign up| Signup[Sign up form]
    Signup --> CreateOrg[Create business / clinic]
    CreateOrg --> VerifyEmail[Send email verification]
    VerifyEmail --> EmailConfirmed{Email confirmed?}
    EmailConfirmed -->|No| VerifyEmail
    EmailConfirmed -->|Yes| OwnerRole[Assign Owner role]
    OwnerRole --> Onboarded{Onboarding complete?}
    Onboarded -->|No| Onboarding[/Setup wizard — see onboarding.mmd/]
    Onboarding --> Dashboard
    Onboarded -->|Yes| Dashboard

    %% --- Invited user accepting an invite ---
    Entry -->|Invite link| AcceptInvite[Open invitation]
    AcceptInvite --> InviteValid{Invite valid / not expired?}
    InviteValid -->|No| InviteError[Show expired/invalid] --> End
    InviteValid -->|Yes| SetPassword[Set name + password]
    SetPassword --> MarkVerified[Mark email verified<br/>invite link proves ownership]
    MarkVerified --> InviteRole[Assign invited role: Admin or Staff]
    InviteRole --> RoleGate

    %% --- Returning user login ---
    Entry -->|Log in| Login[Login form]
    Login --> AuthCheck{Email + password valid?}
    AuthCheck -->|No| LoginError[Show error] --> Login
    AuthCheck -->|Yes| EmailVerified{Email verified?}
    EmailVerified -->|No| VerifyEmail
    EmailVerified -->|Yes| RoleGate

    %% --- Role gating ---
    RoleGate{Role?}
    RoleGate -->|Owner| Onboarded
    RoleGate -->|Admin| Dashboard[Full dashboard]
    RoleGate -->|Staff| StaffView[Limited dashboard]
    RoleGate -->|Suspended| Denied[Access denied] --> End

    Dashboard --> Active([Session active])
    StaffView --> Active
    End([Exit])
